<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Premium Invoice - {{invoice_number}}</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');
        
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        
        .invoice-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .premium-border {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #d4af37, #aa8a2d, #d4af37);
        }
        
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
        }
        
        .company-info h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .company-info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .invoice-info {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .invoice-info h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #d4af37;
        }
        
        .invoice-details {
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .invoice-details div {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .client-info {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .client-info h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .client-details {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        
        .client-details div {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .items-table th {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e8e8e8;
        }
        
        .items-table td {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
        }
        
        .items-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .text-right {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .summary {
            margin-left: auto;
            width: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .summary-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
        }
        
        .summary-row.total {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e8e8e8;
            padding-top: 15px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        
        .payment-info {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .payment-info h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .bank-details {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .bank-details div {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .signatures {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }
        
        .signature-box {
            width: 45%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .signature-line {
            margin-top: 60px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #95a5a6;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        
        .status-paid {
            background-color: #e7f6e9;
            color: #2e7d32;
        }
        
        .status-pending {
            background-color: #ffecb3;
            color: #f57c00;
        }
        
        .status-overdue {
            background-color: #ffcdd2;
            color: #c62828;
        }
        
        .status-draft {
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            color: #424242;
        }
        
        .watermark {
            position: absolute;
            opacity: 0.03;
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
            transform: rotate(-45deg);
            top: 40%;
            left: 20%;
            z-index: -1;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="invoice-container">
        <div class="premium-border"></div>
        <div class="watermark">PREMIUM</div>
        
        <div class="header">
            <div class="company-info">
                <h1>Your Company Name</h1>
                <p>123 Business Avenue, Suite 456</p>
                <p>New York, NY 10001</p>
                <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>
                <p>Email: info@yourcompany.com</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="invoice-info">
                <h2>INVOICE</h2>
                <div class="invoice-details">
                    <div><strong>Invoice Number:</strong> {{invoice_number}}</div>
                    <div><strong>Issue Date:</strong> {{date}}</div>
                    <div><strong>Due Date:</strong> {{due_date}}</div>
                    <div><strong>Status:</strong> 
                        <span class="status-badge status-{{status}}">{{status}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="client-info">
            <h3>Bill To</h3>
            <div class="client-details">
                <div>
                    <strong>{{client_name}}</strong><br>
                    {{client_email}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <table class="items-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Description</th>
                    <th>Quantity</th>
                    <th>Unit Price</th>
                    <th class="text-right">Amount</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#each items}}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{description}}</td>
                    <td class="text-center">{{quantity}}</td>
                    <td>{{price}} {{../currency}}</td>
                    <td class="text-right">{{multiply quantity price}} {{../currency}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/each}}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <div class="summary">
            <div class="summary-row">
                <div>Subtotal:</div>
                <div>{{amount}} {{currency}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="summary-row">
                <div>Tax (0%):</div>
                <div>{{calculateTax amount 0}} {{currency}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="summary-row total">
                <div>TOTAL:</div>
                <div>{{amount}} {{currency}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="payment-info">
            <h3>Payment Information</h3>
            <div class="bank-details">
                <div>
                    <strong>Bank Transfer:</strong><br>
                    Bank Name: Your Bank Name<br>
                    Account Number: 1234 5678 9012 3456<br>
                    Routing Number: 021000021
                </div>
                <div>
                    <strong>Other Methods:</strong><br>
                    PayPal: payments@yourcompany.com<br>
                    Credit Card: Via secure payment link
                </div>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-style: italic;">
                Please include invoice number {{invoice_number}} with your payment.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="signatures">
            <div class="signature-box">
                <div class="signature-line">Authorized Signature</div>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-box">
                <div class="signature-line">Client Signature</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for your business. Payment is due within {{daysBetween date due_date}} days of issue date.</p>
            <p>Questions? Email billing@yourcompany.com or call (123) 456-7890 during business hours.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>